snippet.title: Dino Galaxy Tennis - Steam Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Dino Galaxy Tennis on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1454080

Dino Galaxy Tennis is a 2D side-view action tennis game set in space on the surface of various planets.
You take on the role of dinosaurs that have unique skills to strike, maneuver, and power up comets that are able to destroy worlds!

Play solo in the full-fledged campaign mode where you play against other galactic Dinos and even against the whole planets. 

You can also complete the campaign or try Versus and Challenges features with your friends via a dedicated Co-op modes.
